First off, the service here was great!
The guy at the counter was friendly and cool.
Now for the icecream - it was regular, nothing special.
Looking at the display case, nothing unusual or particularly tempting called out to me, so I ordered a half scoop of cookies and cream with a half scoop of dark chocolate.
It was yummy, but icecream is always yummy.
I wanted that something more that would make this place worth returning to, and I didn't find it.
Ways this place could improve - offer more toppings.
